text: Gopal Tamang (Nepali: गोपाल तामाङ) is a Nepalese politician and a member of the Koshi Provincial Assembly from Nepali Congress. He was elected via 2022 Provincial Assembly election from Jhapa 1 (A). == References == Category:Nepalese politicians Category:Nepali Congress politicians from Koshi Province Category:Tamang people
title: Gopal Tamang
